  "short_description": "Immerse yourself in Soulkin, a tactical, monster-collecting Roguelite. Play as Nadia, a heroine summoned to save the world of Ankiril. Collect unique Soulkin, engage in strategic, turn-based battles on a hex grid, and defeat powerful foes to unlock new content and stop the corruption on Ankiril.",
