  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soulkin is a tactical, Roguelite game that blends strategic monster-collecting with turn-based combat. As the summoned heroine, Nadia, you’ll harness the power of Souls to bond with magical creatures and lead them against the encroaching corruption threatening Ankiril. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This mystical world, anchored around a colossal tree, teems with magical creatures known as Soulkin, each infused with the power of elements. Will you rise to the challenge and become the savior of Ankiril?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/ab10aa31352887e1ae2a954eeb08883c.webp?t=1763460378\" width=600 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/6559538d233b453f91c19b61073e2d76.poster.avif?t=1763460378\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/6559538d233b453f91c19b61073e2d76.webm?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/6559538d233b453f91c19b61073e2d76.mp4?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in turn-based battles that require tactical positioning and clever use of your Soulkin’ abilities. Adapt your tactics to overcome formidable foes and environmental challenges on a hexagonal grid.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/31a5e3953a58b686aeabff278419f3e3.webp?t=1763460378\" width=600 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/11b534c68c3a163588ae64e47c9d328a.poster.avif?t=1763460378\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/11b534c68c3a163588ae64e47c9d328a.webm?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/11b534c68c3a163588ae64e47c9d328a.mp4?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from multiple Soulkin squads and Nadia variants, each boasting distinct elemental strengths and playstyles. As you complete objectives, you’ll unlock new squads, additional power-ups, and stronger abilities. Strategically choose and enhance your squad to confront Ankiril’s ever-growing threats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/b6c50fb35da4e976ff73f04cb849fe32.webp?t=1763460378\" width=600 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/b5864bf5bab69494a80adddc70977d35.poster.avif?t=1763460378\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/b5864bf5bab69494a80adddc70977d35.webm?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/b5864bf5bab69494a80adddc70977d35.mp4?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through challenging encounters and unlock new events, bonuses, and increased stats. Your journey will be difficult, but the rewards are plentiful for those who persevere.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/ff38da1971fafcefbf657387faef958e.webp?t=1763460378\" width=600 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/551cceea1943a0271c1a2a6873da72f9.poster.avif?t=1763460378\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/551cceea1943a0271c1a2a6873da72f9.webm?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/551cceea1943a0271c1a2a6873da72f9.mp4?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each chapter offers a fresh and unique gameplay experience with dynamic maps, battles, and events. This ensures varied and exciting playthroughs every time, keeping the gameplay engaging and unpredictable. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/b7a8908136cf14e0903f2bd1a677db04.avif?t=1763460378\" width=600 height=146 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soulkin is a tactical, Roguelite game that blends strategic monster-collecting with turn-based combat. As the summoned heroine, Nadia, you’ll harness the power of Souls to bond with magical creatures and lead them against the encroaching corruption threatening Ankiril. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This mystical world, anchored around a colossal tree, teems with magical creatures known as Soulkin, each infused with the power of elements. Will you rise to the challenge and become the savior of Ankiril?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/ab10aa31352887e1ae2a954eeb08883c.webp?t=1763460378\" width=600 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/6559538d233b453f91c19b61073e2d76.poster.avif?t=1763460378\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/6559538d233b453f91c19b61073e2d76.webm?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/extras/6559538d233b453f91c19b61073e2d76.mp4?t=1763460378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in turn-based battles that require tactical positioning and clever use of your Soulkin’ abilities. Adapt your tactics to overcome formidable foes and environmental challenges on a hexagonal grid.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849070/e